cards.rules_text:
When Slayer's Mantle enters, create a 1/1 white Angel creature token with flying, then attach Slayer's Mantle to it.
Equipped creature has base power and toughness 3/3 and has flying and first strike.
Equip {2}

Whenever Heirloom Bauble enters or equipped creature dies, put a novelty counter on it.
{1}, Sacrifice Heirloom Bauble: Draw cards equal to the number of novelty counters on it.
Equip {1}

When Wanderer's Trinkets enters, return up to two target creatures to their owners' hand.
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, draw two cards, then discard a card.
Equip {2}

Equipped creature gets +1/+1.
When equipped creature dies, you may sacrifice Soulful Flower. If you do, create two 1/1 green Scout creature tokens.
Equip {1}

When Bloodied Armor enters, you may pay 3 life or sacrifice a creature. When you do, attach it to target creature you control.
Equipped creature gets +2/+2.
Equip {3}

When Fishing Rod enters, create a 1/1 green Scout creature token, then attach Fishing Rod to it.
Equipped creature has “{T}: Surveil 1.” [i](To surveil 1, look at the top card of your library. You may put it into your graveyard.)[/i]
Equip {3}

When Traveler's Cloak enters, you may search your library for a basic land card, reveal it, then shuffle and put that card on top.
Equipped creature gets +1/+1.
Equip {1}

When Full Kit enters, create a 1/1 green Scout creature token, then attach Full Kit to it.
Equipped creature gets +2/+1.
Equip {3}

Whenever a creature that shares a creature type with equipped creature enters under your control, draw a card.
{1}, Sacrifice Mask of Communion: Equipped creature gains hexproof until end of turn.
Equip {2}

Equipped creature gets +2/+2.
Whenever equipped creature dies, you may pay 2 life. If you do, create a 1/1 white Soldier creature token.
Equip {2}

Whenever equipped creature attacks, it and another target creature you control each gain +2/+1 until end of turn.
Equip Scout {1}
Equip {3}

Whenever Essence Cloak becomes attached to a nontoken creature, exile that creature, then create a token that's a copy of it and attach Essence Cloak to it.
Equipped creature gets +1/+1 for each card exiled with Essence Cloak.
Equip {2}

When Rallier's Plate enters, return target creature card with mana value 3 or less from your graveyard to the battlefield, then attach Rallier's Plate to that creature.
Whenever equipped creature attacks, creatures you control get +1/+1 until end of turn.
Equip {2}

Equipped creature has protection from triggered abilities.
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, when you next trigger one or more abilities that aren't mana abilities this turn, copy one of them. You may choose new targets for the copy.
Equip {1}
